 />\n求下你地幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce419442e9f1af0b3c273c8db18b19b4d8b554b5","tid":298071,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"負評上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b47c9a3ff4f74f38ba0794ae9d809f3380292c8","tid":298071,"uid":19874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1a356175fd46a7bb3721663f24627745acc4b7","tid":298071,"uid":35373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 小弟我最近想玩返p&amp;d （因為無啦啦好多朋友叫我玩）同埋聽講出左協力 多人玩左又好玩左 所以想搵返以前個account<br />\n<br />\n跟住我就上網睇教學跟住做 ：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/115330_9fe93824f5ac043f48c6c94df07ccc35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F115330_9fe93824f5ac043f48c6c94df07ccc35.jpg&h=92e872d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/115342_1fbfd1793f7d237f51a926295962b733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F115342_1fbfd1793f7d237f51a926295962b733.jpg&h=4da34b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload